title: Yum Could Take Chinese Food to Go
text:
Will the stars be favorable for Yum Brands Inc.?
The Year of the Goat, which lasts another five months, is supposed to be a prosperous one according to Chinese astrology. It certainly hasn’t been for the American fast food giant’s huge Chinese operations, dominated by KFC. Same-store sales so far this fiscal year have fallen by more than 10% versus the prior one.
